<claim-text><highlight><bold>78</bold></highlight>. The process of <dependent-claim-reference depends_on="CLM-00055">claim 55</dependent-claim-reference>, wherein said at least one transition metal ion species is copper (II).</claim-text>
</claim>
</subdoc-claims>
