<subdoc-abstract>
<paragraph id="A-0001" lvl="0">A bioengineered synthesis scheme for the production of quinic acid from a carbon source is provided. Methods of producing quinic acid from a earbon source based on the synthesis scheme as well as conversion of quinic acid to hydroquinone are also provided. </paragraph>
</subdoc-abstract>
<subdoc-description>
<cross-reference-to-related-applications>
